title: Turrican II - The Final Fight Gamerip
description:
From the .nfo:


One day, I noticed that someone had made
a gamerip of Turrican II, "Cool!" I thought, until
I downloaded that rip in question... The bitrate sucked
and the tracks were cut short, in my rip the tracks at least
get to start the second loop.


It's the one and only gamerip I've made.
It's not perfect, but it's good enough for me to listen.
